text: The House of Representatives of the Federation of Bosnia and Herzegovina is the lower house of the Parliament of the Federation of Bosnia and Herzegovina, the legislative body of the Federation of Bosnia and Herzegovina, one of two entities of Bosnia and Herzegovina.Parliament of the Federation ==References== ==Other websites== *Constitution of Bosnia Herzegovina 1995 (rev. 2009) Category:Government of Bosnia and Herzegovina Category:Legislatures of country subdivisions
title: House of Representatives of the Federation of Bosnia and Herzegovina
